'''medui''' means "last" in [[Sindarin]]

==Etymology==
[[Old Sindarin]] word *''metâja'' < [[Sundocarmë|Root]] [[MET]] 

It contains the ending [[-ui]].
==Other forms==
[[lenition|Lenited]] forms:
*'''-vedui''' in the expression '''na-vedui''' "at last"
*''[[Arvedui#Etymology|Ar'''vedui''']]'' "Last King".
